Q:

determine maximum number of days in particular month

from razor view I'm sending selected month and year to the controller using jquery. Inside controller I'm receiving those selected values and create datetime properties 
public ActionResult Index(int year, int month)
{
 Date1 = new DateTime(year, month, 1);
 Date2 = new DateTime(year, month, 31);
 ...
}

Some months has 31 day, some 30 and feb. has 28 (inside leap year 29) days. My question is: 
How can I recognize those months and based on that set appropriate max month day inside Date2 variable? A:

You could use the DaysInMonth method on DateTime:
Date2 = new DateTime(year, month, DateTime.DaysInMonth(year, month));

